answerText: Park Guell[10] The Nativity Facade is one side of this other building by Antoni Gaudi, an experimental cathedral with eighteen spires that has an estimated completion date of 2026.

question: Question: This locale is situated on the El Carmel hill. For 10 points each: [10] Name this complex of buildings and gardens, whose central portion features a serpent-shaped bench. Its entrance is marked by a multicolored salamander called "el drac."
